{"tid":1050507,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「E-的士」網約平台上半年推出","createTime":"2019-03-07T02:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T03:41:20.000Z","uid":56881,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0d5ebc3ee9a7bd3718f7d6c6eec4fb8b8a60957c","tid":1050507,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/e-%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%84%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA-223000516.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fe-%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B4%2584%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%2587%25BA-223000516.html&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QEXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=ccb344b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/e-%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB-%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%84%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA-223000516.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_yHAajHr63WIoPsTvi.KgA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzQwO2g9MjU1O2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/75721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_yHAajHr63WIoPsTvi.KgA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzQwO2g9MjU1O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F75721.jpg&h=404279b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n議會主席熊永達（前排中）宣布，將會推出「E-的士」應用程式。<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】網約車平台Uber香港前日宣布與一間的士車行合作推出「Uber Flash」叫車服務，引起的士業界不滿，最終該的士車行「縮沙」。香港的士業議會昨公布正自資開發全新的士網約平台「E-的士」應用程式，現有近千名的士司機加入，預料於今年上半年推出，市民可透過程式即時或預約叫車，備有車資提示功能，乘客上車前已知道估算車資，而為鼓勵的士司機承接短途車程，司機可獲得積分，兌換獎品甚至獎金。<br />\n<br />\nUber早前透露將與本港一間的士車行合作，在指定程式中可召喚的士服務，引來三十八個的士團體聯署反對。香港的士業議會昨公布將會推出「E-的士」應用程式，反擊Uber。議會主席熊永達表示，由十多個的士組織及贊助商出資開發有關程式，期望今年上半年推出，屆時用戶可透過手機應用程式預約的士，並可選擇車款、司機及行車路線等，目前已有近千名司機參與。<br />\n<br />\n熊永達強調，「E-的士」符合本港法例，將比Uber提供較佳服務，如程式可向司機發放實時交通消息，方便規劃路線駕駛，司機亦可透過程式承接電召服務乘客等，而程式不會向司機及乘客收取任何附加費。至於外界一直批評的士司機經常拒載，熊永達指，新程式設有積分制度，鼓勵司機承接短途、坐輪椅或攜帶動物等的乘客，當司機儲到足夠分數時，可換取汽油券等禮品。<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係DC9既態度<br />\n出幾多個APP都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3588eacebaa870c6658a241f1cb69a4128014af6","tid":1050507,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:51:48.000Z","msg":"佢地認為uber多人用只因有app?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2daad04779534ead870f7b1e7f5aef4f88f660f9","tid":1050507,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:53:29.000Z","msg":"由鳩佢啦 到時好用咪用 唔好用咪算"},{"pid":"6853fb39fcbd24d1c21aecdc28fd4fc79a221ca5","tid":1050507,"uid":8392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:11:43.000Z","msg":"真係唔知自己衰乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28a84ace557c6c8ea9c334896e70f34b7765298","tid":1050507,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2daad04779534ead870f7b1e7f5aef4f88f660f9","tid":1050507,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T02:53:29.000Z","msg":"由鳩佢啦 到時好用咪用 唔好用咪算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:15:48.000Z","msg":"好唔好用都唔坐的士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf362bf1e333e549fd39840c50101f696aa7ddd","tid":1050507,"uid":67294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:15:57.000Z","msg":"到時個app整個&quot;+$20&quot; &quot;+$50&quot; 既制有得優先<br />\n之後一大堆唔過海既直接寫 not available in your region<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a4ec21f5f4b2c446996336f4eb63bb7a4ba452","tid":1050507,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T03:23:24.000Z","msg":"坊間一大堆taxi app啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486b8b7fe6dffedea629b26273496334ea1ab42a","tid":1050507,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu